<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_8b8d3535-5d8e-4bd1-adaa-6f06aa53634c" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>12.4.4</sptc><title id="_0c552466-0068-4815-a94b-b903e332a581">Installation of insert fireplaces and flues</title><archive-num>2019: 3.10.7.4</archive-num><subclause id="_d0445c3d-ac35-4953-b7b6-5a07586d0d17" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_f7f3e89e-dd6d-472b-af45-aca6056a3803">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>An insert fireplace and flue must comply with the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_8082e185-ff13-41fd-8196-d6430826d723">The insert fireplace and flue must be— <ol><li>tested and passed the tests required by AS/NZS 2918; and</li><li>fitted into a masonry fireplace (including chimney) constructed in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/1807#_c1e7a2da-3ebf-4007-9f08-134efafe0279" id="_306c690a-e2c8-4053-a711-7ebbdb1e5abe" publishing-id="vol2" scope="external" type="clause">H1D5</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4609_0.8.0.xml#_6a2d818e-ce79-4b1b-bf99-909a10a02a8d" id="_5b5a69d6-0744-4b85-bbdb-2d720ac558f8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 12.4.4</xref>.</li></ol></li><li id="_5b43bfc0-3c24-4fad-a552-7f92b6bad7fc">The flue must be double skin and have been tested and pass the tests required by AS/NZS 2918.</li><li id="_b818b7d7-e719-422a-96bf-ef9751b04b60">There must be a clearance of 50 mm between the outer flue and adjacent materials.</li><li id="_87362d0c-ce07-4da5-8905-d521c86a4a99">The flue must terminate in accordance with <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/906_0.7.0.xml#_2e89ef8e-308b-411f-b5a9-81503d82271c" id="_1f9d6793-cc92-4333-b22f-dd6e206f71a4" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 12.4.3</xref>.</li><li id="_f9ae9a8c-1ec0-4818-89e5-868d35a010b3">The hearth must be constructed in accordance with <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/2661_1.7.0.xml#_ef86e29f-51cb-46c5-a25e-413f5188dfba" id="_edbe5206-4f2d-4ab1-9ea5-9a6cb9d8ed23" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="clause">12.4.2(b)</xref> and <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/2661_1.7.0.xml#_ef86e29f-51cb-46c5-a25e-413f5188dfba" id="_a2b31bae-4443-45da-9adf-ef2361aa907c" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="clause">(d)</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><image-reference author="Brandon Kiem" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/4609_0.8.0.xml" dateTime="2021-02-24T10:56:51" id="_6a2d818e-ce79-4b1b-bf99-909a10a02a8d" type="insert"><num>12.4.4</num><title id="_e6fd74f5-29bf-43d5-86da-7e6e82aae0ed">Typical installation of fireplace flue inserts</title><image alt="Typical installation of fireplace flue inserts" height="1284" heightdpi="200" href="ERROR_IN_RESOLVING_URI:12-4-4-typical-installation-of-fireplace-flue-inserts.eps" width="1200" widthdpi="200"><image height="1284" heightdpi="200" href="C:\Users\bkiem\AppData\Roaming\Quark\XML Author\Temp\media1_33c3dee4-f021-4316-90a8-58677fa0c7fc.jpg" width="1200" widthdpi="200"/></image></image-reference></clause>